le=Fracture+and+fatigue+control+in+structures+%3A+applications+of+fracture+mechanics&amp;rft.place=West+Conshohocken%2C+Pa.&amp;rft.edition=3.&amp;rft.pub=ASTM&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.isbn=0803120826&amp;rft.aulast=Rolfe&amp;rft.aufirst=John+M.+Barsom%2C+Stanley+T.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFracture" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li> <li id="cite_note-Campbell-6"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Campbell_6-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Campbell_6-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Campbell_6-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Campbell_6-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Campbell_6-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Campbell_6-5"><sup><i><b>f</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Campbell_6-6"><sup><i><b>g</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Campbell_6-7"><sup><i><b>h</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation book">Campbell, edited by F.C. (2012). <i>Fatigue and fracture&#160;: understanding the basics</i>. Materials Park, Ohio: ASM International. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/1615039767" title="Special:BookSources/1615039767">1615039767</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Fatigue+and+fracture+%3A+understanding+the+basics&amp;rft.place=Materials+Park%2C+Ohio&amp;rft.pub=ASM+International&amp;rft.date=2012&amp;rft.isbn=1615039767&amp;rft.aulast=Campbell&amp;rft.aufirst=edited+by+F.C.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFracture" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span><span class="citation-comment" style="display:none; color:#33aa33; margin-left:0.3em">CS1 maint: Extra text: authors list (<a href="/wiki/Category:CS1_maint:_Extra_text:_authors_list" title="Category:CS1 maint: Extra text: authors list">link</a>)</span></span></li> <li id="cite_note-7"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-7">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation journal">C. H. Chen; H. P. Zhang; J. Niemczura; K. Ravi-Chandar; M. Marder (November 2011). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://iopscience.iop.org/0295-5075/96/3/36009/">"Scaling of crack propagation in rubber sheets"</a>. <i>Europhysics Letters</i>. <b>96</b> (3): 36009. <a href="/wiki/Bibcode" title="Bibcode">Bibcode</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2011EL.....9636009C">2011EL.....9636009C</a>. <a href="/wiki/Digital_object_identifier" title="Digital object identifier">doi</a>:<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="//doi.org/10.1209%2F0295-5075%2F96%2F36009">10.1209/0295-5075/96/36009</a>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Europhysics+Letters&amp;rft.atitle=Scaling+of+crack+propagation+in+rubber+sheets&amp;rft.volume=96&amp;rft.issue=3&amp;rft.pages=36009&amp;rft.date=2011-11&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1209%2F0295-5075%2F96%2F36009&amp;rft_id=info%3Abibcode%2F2011EL.....9636009C&amp;rft.au=C.+H.+Chen&amp;rft.au=H.+P.+Zhang&amp;rft.au=J.+Niemczura&amp;rft.au=K.+Ravi-Chandar&amp;rft.au=M.+Marder&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fiopscience.iop.org%2F0295-5075%2F96%2F3%2F36009%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFracture" class="Z3988"><span style="display:none;">&#160;</span></span></span></li> <li id="cite_note-8"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-8">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite class="citation book">Perez, Nestor (2016). <i>Fracture Mechanics</i> (2nd ed.). Springer. <a href="/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number" title="International Standard Book Number">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/3319249975